planSettings.description:
Short for Power Hypertrophy Upper Lower, PHUL blends power and size building principles for the athlete looking to get stronger and bigger.

The PHUL program follows many of the principles of powerbuilding programming, but could also be considered a bodybuilding program.

Program taken from: https://liftvault.com/programs/strength/phul-spreadsheet/


Features:

  1. 6 Days of workouts
  2. Automatic calculation of weight per set


How to use:

The first week is to enter your 1 Rep Maxs to provide data for the rest of the program which starts in week 2. If you have your 1RM already enter them in and start the week a week earlier.
